name: .22 SUMY NONA ZINE LEAF-THRU editie 13.0/14.0 jan/feb
description:
this is a video of myself holding the zine on my lap and flipping through the whole thing. it really gives a better idea of what it actually looks like vs the pdf.
10/10 accessory NFT to the zine.
minted on a split contract that benefits every artist that submitted if they have a tezos wallet & the rest for non-wallet people is set aside in a catch-all wallet to benefit artists some other way in the future. will probably vote on what to do with those. so far this is all conceptual until people buy the NFTs. so please do. #web3
